  "detailed_description": "Undead Souls is an arcade game about killing enemies trying to Beat your Score in a gun filled randomly generated levels.<br><br>In this version of the game you will have the option to challenge yourself trying to beat your score. In this game you will enter an environment randomly generated with full of enemies and try to kill as many as you can.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667170/extras/434c8b15391948d9bbc7f800448308df.avif?t=1711257915\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br><br><strong>Features and Content</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Levels with different themes and enemies<br></li><li>  All level are procedurally and ramdomly generated to add more randomness to each gameplay ( Every game is different - random levels ).</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667170/extras/30a1c1fec16645cc3e714f8eb94789ff.avif?t=1711257915\" width=600 height=282 /></span>",
